        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Make wader repairs waterside or at camp with the handy Aquaseal FD Repair Kit. With a 0.25 oz tube of Aquaseal FD adhesive, 3” Tenacious Tape Repair Patches (one clear and one black nylon), a brush and instructions, holes and tears won’t stop the outdoor fun. This patch kit permanently fixes torn waders, drysuits, and low PSI inflatables. Enclosed in a lightweight and compact container, it’s easy to pack along in case rips happen to neoprene, vinyl, nylon, and GORE-TEX gear. So, get a waterproof repair that lasts and bring the Aquaseal FD Repair Kit along on the next adventure.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
